# Door component substitutes
#
# Place a SketchUp door .skp here. consume_consensus.rb defaults to
# `Door Interior.skp` (Trimble SU sampler) but any single-leaf door
# component works as long as `assume_upright` is set correctly in
# place_door_component.rb.
#
# Sources for substitute components (2026-04-25):
# - C:/ProgramData/SketchUp/SketchUp 2026/SketchUp/Components/Components Sampler/Door Interior.skp
#   (local install, recommended; copied here on 2026-04-25)
# - https://3dwarehouse.sketchup.com (search "porta interior")
# - https://builtarchi.com/sketchup-door-model/ (free Door_3D_model_1.skp)
# - https://www.allanbrito.com/2016/11/29/portas-e-janelas-para-sketchup-download-gratuito/
#
# *.skp files in this folder are gitignored to avoid redistributing
# Trimble sampler components without explicit license clearance.
